---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout>
  <section>
    <h1>Projects</h1>

    <article>
      <h2>BNYM Corporation – IR2: GTT (Good To Transact)</h2>
      <p><strong>Environment</strong>: React, React Hooks, Redux, Node.js, TypeScript, HTML5, CSS3, Spring MVC/Boot, Java</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Enterprise app for creating and approving rate requests; integrated with RWH, ECIF, GCG, MSC via Nexen framework.</li>
        <li>Modules: New Rate Request, Tracker, Shell Requests, Manage Accounts, Bid Flow with multi-stage approvals to 100% completion.</li>
        <li>Built unified forms to replace multiple screens; delivered KPI reporting using Denodo and ThoughtSpot (IR2: GTT, MSC, IMMS, Deal Manager & RWH).</li>
      </ul>
    </article>

    <article>
      <h2>Sprint – ReArch</h2>
      <p><strong>Environment</strong>: React, Node.js, HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript, Spring MVC/Boot, Java</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Migrated legacy system to a modern architecture with Angular/React.</li>
        <li>Supported front-office and back-office workflows to sell devices and voice plans.</li>
        <li>Worked in Agile; clarified functional and non-functional characteristics and authored design documentation.</li>
      </ul>
    </article>

    <article>
      <h2>UPS – QVMC & eTT</h2>
      <p><strong>Environment</strong>: HTML5, CSS3, Mainframe, Angular 2/4, Node.js, React, jQuery</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Migrated tracking app from Flex to Angular/Java for inbound/outbound logistics.</li>
        <li>Implemented performant data grids and customized Angular components to UPS standards.</li>
      </ul>
    </article>

    <article>
      <h2>AIG – Travel Guard</h2>
      <p><strong>Environment</strong>: UX, HTML5, CSS3, AngularJS, Bootstrap, SASS</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Automated customer claim forms and built AngularJS forms with Bootstrap.</li>
        <li>Introduced SASS workflow to generate modular, maintainable CSS.</li>
      </ul>
    </article>

    <article>
      <h2>British Telecom – Odyssey Search</h2>
      <p><strong>Environment</strong>: HTML, XSLT, XML, jQuery, CSS, ZXTM traffic script, Ant, Photoshop</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Developed search tooling for BT broadband customers using XHTML/XSLT.</li>
        <li>Coordinated demos with Google and BT stakeholders prior to production release.</li>
      </ul>
    </article>

    <article>
      <h2>Cisco – Flex Service Retainers, Emerging Markets</h2>
      <p><strong>Environment</strong>: Photoshop, HTML, JavaScript, CSS, Dreamweaver</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Migrated sites to new Cisco standards and CMS; created reusable UI components.</li>
        <li>Collaborated with marketing on feedback cycles to improve UI processes.</li>
      </ul>
    </article>
  </section>
</Layout>
